- Boy:
FIVE, SIX, SEVEN...

9
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:12,375
OH!  HEY, MAMA!
IT'S PAPA!

10
00:02:13,458 --> 00:02:16,333
- ( engine stops )
- HEY, I'M HOME, HENRI.

11
00:02:16,416 --> 00:02:18,500
- YAY!  PAPA IS HOME!

12
00:02:18,583 --> 00:02:21,666
- YOU'RE EARLY.  WE WEREN'T
EXPECTING YOU FOR HOURS

13
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:25,541
- YEAH, TODAY'S CASELOAD
WAS PRETTY LIGHT.

14
00:02:26,625 --> 00:02:28,541
LOUIS' STILL ASLEEP, HUH?

15
00:02:28,625 --> 00:02:31,875
- ( chuckles ) NO, HE'S BEEN
CRYING ALL DAY LONG,

16
00:02:31,958 --> 00:02:34,958
AND I JUST GOT THE LITTLE
MONSTER SETTLED DOWN.

17
00:02:35,041 --> 00:02:37,666
- ( laughs ) REALLY?
- YES, REALLY.

18
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,041
- AND BY THE WAY, HENRI,

19
