A POLICE OFFICER

57
00:05:29,125 --> 00:05:30,666
WHO GAVE HIS LIFE
FOR HIS COUNTRY.

58
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:33,125
- I KNOW THAT.

59
00:05:33,208 --> 00:05:35,041
- THIS IS THE THIRD ONE.

60
00:05:35,125 --> 00:05:37,500
