67
00:05:57,291 --> 00:05:59,208
- HMM.

68
00:05:59,291 --> 00:06:02,083
- AT THE VERY LEAST,
I WANT A REPORT READIED

69
00:06:02,166 --> 00:06:03,958
FOR THE MINISTRY
OF NATIONAL DEFENSE

70
00:06:04,041 --> 00:06:06,250
ON THAT SUBJECT.
