71
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:07,958
- UNDERSTOOD.

72
00:06:08,041 --> 00:06:09,541
I'LL START ON IT
IMMEDIATELY, SIR.

73
00:06:10,666 --> 00:06:12,916
- TOP SECRET.
- RIGHT.

74
00:06:18,166 --> 00:06:20,208
- ( sighs )
- ( bell tolling )

75
00:06:25,541 --> 00:06:29,625
- I JUST PRAY THAT OUR FEARS
TURN OUT TO BE UNFOUNDED.

76
00:06:31,833 --> 00:06:34,333
- YES SIR.
I'LL BE PRAYING AS WELL.

77
00:06:48,041 --> 00:06:49,333
