AS THOUGH YOU'RE ENJOYING IT?

90
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,875
- I AM ENJOYING IT.

91
00:08:31,958 --> 00:08:34,125
- WELL, YOU DON'T LOOK
LIKE YOU ARE.

92
00:08:34,208 --> 00:08:36,708
- REALLY?
- ( emphatically ) REALLY.

93
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:57,250
- AND YOU DON'T REMEMBER
ANYTHING ABOUT YOURSELF?

94
00:08:57,333 --> 00:09:00,333
- MM-HMM.
- WHAT ABOUT ME?

95
00:09:06,666 --> 00:09:08,250
- MIREILLE BOUQUET,

96
00:09:08,333 --> 00:09:11,291
