ALL BEEN EXECUTED.

111
00:11:10,458 --> 00:11:13,750
THAT'S THREE LESS
G.I.G.N. DOGS TO HARRY US.

112
00:11:15,125 --> 00:11:17,041
THERE'S NO FOOL LIKE
A FEROCIOUS DOG

113
00:11:17,125 --> 00:11:19,375
THAT'S BLINDLY LOYAL
TO HIS MASTER.

114
00:11:19,458 --> 00:11:21,041
- MMM.

115
00:11:21,125 --> 00:11:24,708
- YOU ARE CONTRIBUTING
TO THE FUTURE OF FRANCE

116
00:11:24,791 --> 00:11:26,833
BY WEEDING OUT THOSE FOOLS.

117
00:11:28,083 --> 00:11:29,291
- AND THE MONEY?

118
00:11:29,375 --> 00:11:31,041
- THE USUAL.

119
00:11:31,125 --> 00:11:33,375
WHAT ABOUT
THE PUBLIC PEACE DEPARTMENT?

120
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:36,000
- DON'T WORRY.
I'M WITH YOU.

121
00:11:36,083 --> 00:11:39,583
- GOOD.
I'M COUNTING ON YOU, COMRADE.

122
00:11:42,333 --> 00:11:44,041
I'LL SEE YOU AGAIN
NEXT WEEK.

123
00:11:48,166 --> 00:11:51,250
- Mireille: OUR TARGETS
ARE JEAN JACQUES LEGRAND,

124
00:11:51,333 --> 00:11:53,958
DIRECTOR OF THE FRENCH NATIONAL
PUBLIC PEACE DEPARTMENT,

125
00:11:54,041 --> 00:11:57,041
AND PIERRE CRESSOY,
A KEY OFFICER

126
00:11:57,125 --> 00:11:59,583
IN THE LEADING FACTION
OF THE PEOPLE'S ARMED ALLIANCE--

127
00:11:59,666 --> 00:12:01,833
A FAR-RIGHT
TERRORIST ORGANIZATION.

128
00:12:01,916 --> 00:12:05,375
