LEGRAND RECEIVED INFORMATION

130
00:12:08,333 --> 00:12:10,833
FROM CRESSOY THAT IMPROVED
HIS CONVICTION RATE.

131
00:12:10,916 --> 00:12:14,083
OUR CLIENT IS ANOTHER FACTION
OF THE PEOPLE'S ARMED ALLIANCE.

132
00:12:14,166 --> 00:12:17,125
THEY WERE RATHER BURNED BY
THE INFORMATION CRESSOY LEAKED.

133
00:12:17,208 --> 00:12:18,875
SO BY HIRING US,

134
00:12:18,958 --> 00:12:21,000
THEY ELIMINATE THE LEADER
OF THEIR RIVAL FACTION

135
00:12:21,083 --> 00:12:22,666
AND LEGRAND IN ONE SHOT.

136
00:12:31,125 --> 00:12:34,125
WELL, TO BE FRANK,
ALL OF THEM ARE SCUM,

137
00:12:34,208 --> 00:12:37,083
BUT THE CLEANING FEE
IS <i>TRES BON.</i>

138
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,875
- ( rock music plays )

139
00:12:58,083 --> 00:12:59,041
- HMM.

140
00:13:12,791 --> 00:13:14,708
- ( chattering )

141
00:13:16,708 --> 00:13:18,250
- THERE HE IS.

142
00:13:21,916 --> 00:13:24,333
WELL, IT APPEARS
OUR CLIENT IS RIGHT.

143
00:13:24,416 --> 00:13:27,875
THERE'S DEFINITELY A CONNECTION
BETWEEN LEGRAND AND CRESSOY.

144
00:13:38,208 --> 00:13:41,083
THIS IS THE LEADING FACTION'S
SAFE HOUSE.

145
