AGE IS BEYOND ME.

147
00:13:45,375 --> 00:13:46,541
- ( paper rustles )

148
00:13:46,625 --> 00:13:48,958
- THESE ARE THE BLUEPRINTS
FOR THAT BUILDING.

149
00:13:49,041 --> 00:13:51,041
