00:16:25,916 --> 00:16:30,500
- AH.  WELCOME TO
OUR HUMBLE FORTRESS, COMRADE.

167
00:16:30,583 --> 00:16:32,208
- I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE UP TO,

168
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:35,000
