IMPORTANT TO BRING ME HERE.

169
00:16:35,083 --> 00:16:38,416
- OH, IT IS.
- SO WHAT IS IT?

170
00:16:38,500 --> 00:16:40,958
- THE ACTIVITIES
OF ONE OF OUR OTHER FACTIONS

171
00:16:41,041 --> 00:16:42,541
HAS BEEN BOTHERING ME.

172
00:16:42,625 --> 00:16:45,250
SO JUST FOR KICKS,
I CAPTURED ONE OF THEM.

173
00:16:45,333 --> 00:16:47,291
- YOU WHAT?
- THIS WAY.

174
00:16:51,958 --> 00:16:55,291
- HE WAS QUITE TOUGH,
BUT HE SPILLED HIS GUTS.

175
00:16:55,375 --> 00:16:58,875
IN FACT, AN HOUR AGO
HE REVEALED THAT HIS FACTION

176
00:16:58,958 --> 00:17:01,708
HAD HIRED AN ASSASSIN
TO KILL THE TWO OF US.

177
00:17:01,791 --> 00:17:03,541
- YOU'RE SURE OF THIS?

178
00:17:03,625 --> 00:17:07,458
- EHH, IT SOUNDS LIKE SOMETHING
THEY WOULD COME UP WITH.

179
00:17:07,541 --> 00:17:11,250
- I SEE.  AND DID YOU GET
THE ASSASSIN'S NAME?

180
00:17:11,333 --> 00:17:13,791
- YEAH, THE CODENAME IS NOIR.

181
00:17:13,875 --> 00:17:15,791
I'M AFRAID
THAT'S ALL HE KNOWS.

182
00:17:15,875 --> 00:17:17,500
- NOIR?!

183
00:17:17,583 --> 00:17:20,291
NOT THE SAME NOIR.

184
00:17:20,375 --> 00:17:22,750
NO, IT CAN'T BE.

185
00:17:22,833 --> 00:17:24,958
- SO YOU KNOW THE NAME.

186
00:17:25,041 --> 00:17:27,083
- YES, IN FACT, I DO.

187
00:17:27,166 --> 00:17:28,541
YOU SEE, THE NAME NOIR

188
00:17:28,625 --> 00:17:31,125
