MEANING IN THE UNDERWORLD.

189
00:17:31,208 --> 00:17:32,500
- OH.

190
00:17:32,583 --> 00:17:34,458
- IT'S NOT VERY WELL KNOWN,

191
00:17:34,541 --> 00:17:36,875
BUT THE TRUTH IS
THAT OUR OWN POLICE

192
00:17:36,958 --> 00:17:39,666
HAVE HIRED NOIR TO HANDLE
CERTAIN JOBS IN THE PAST,

193
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:43,791
