WAS BACK IN THE 1970s.

194
00:17:43,875 --> 00:17:46,416
- HMM?

195
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:49,833
- SO DOES THIS MEAN THAT
NOIR HAS BECOME ACTIVE AGAIN?

196
00:17:49,916 --> 00:17:54,333
OR IS SOMEONE COMPLETELY
UNRELATED CALLING HIMSELF NOIR?

197
00:18:02,083 --> 00:18:04,333
- ( silenced gunshot )
- ( cries out, groans )

198
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,375
- WELL, NO MATTER
WHO THIS NOIR IS,

199
00:18:10,458 --> 00:18:12,416
