PLENTY OF OPTIONS.

201
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:21,166
DON'T WORRY.  I'LL ASSEMBLE
OUR MEMBERS IMMEDIATELY.

202
00:18:21,250 --> 00:18:22,791
- AND THIS ONE?

203
00:18:25,458 --> 00:18:27,125
- DO WHATEVER YOU WANT.

204
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:28,583
- ( chuckles )

