00:18:32,583 --> 00:18:34,500
- ( rock music playing )

206
00:18:37,916 --> 00:18:38,791
- Both: HUH?

207
00:18:43,375 --> 00:18:45,333
- ( cocks )

208
00:18:45,416 --> 00:18:47,791
- TAKE LEGRAND
TO THE EMERGENCY EXIT.

209
00:18:47,875 --> 00:18:49,458
